  "title": "CMS-based High-yielding Pigeonpea Hybrids",
  "abstract": "Pigeonpea [Cajanus cajan (L.) Millsp.] or Red gram is an important pulse crop of\r\nIndia sown every year on 3.9 m ha. The major pigeonpea growing states in India\r\nare Andhra Pradesh, Gujarat, Karnataka, Madhya Pradesh, Maharashtra, Uttar\r\nPradesh and Uttarakhand.",
